pyTesseractTrainer - Visual tesseract box file editor

Project homepage: http://code.google.com/p/pytesseracttrainer/
Source: http://code.google.com/p/pytesseracttrainer/source/checkout
Licence: GNU General Public License v3

pyTesseractTrainer is editor for tesseract-ocr box files. It written using python and PyGTK library, so it can be built on different platforms.

pyTesseractTrainer is successor of tesseractTrainer.py (http://tesseract-ocr.googlecode.com/files/tesseractTrainer.py)